{"tid":2272351,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"招Bass、Keyboard手長夾","createTime":"2020-11-05T04:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T14:10:08.000Z","uid":34841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7bdd86f63851bdbbe31911691faf57e0247a0cb8","tid":2272351,"uid":34841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:18:23.000Z","msg":"現band已有2 guitar、1 vocal、 1 drum, 25-27歲<br />\n<br />\n咩類型都會玩, 但主要玩Pop, pop rock, 會自己寫歌, 暫時有4首自己歌(有demo), 另外會錄音, cover都會玩下, 會keep住搵show出下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係新蒲崗有自己band房, 近鑽石山地鐵站<br />\n穩定左落黎之後要一齊夾band房租金<br />\n（月租低過市價, 一般在職人士絕對負擔得起）<br />\n夾band時間唔定, 成員都係在職人士, 但多數夜晚<br />\n<br />\n要求係最基本技術、溝通好、有交帶、做好自己個位、有心長夾, 唔hea唔係玩玩下<br />\n<br />\n技術可以慢慢練, 最重要係態度<br />\n<br />\n如果有keyboard手, 想加入都歡迎聯絡<br />\n<br />\n有意請留Contact, 謝絕藍人(中立冷感都係)<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc94856ac623e892982c6e17a9884bc47463a3b","tid":2272351,"uid":25582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T10:45:04.000Z","msg":"利嘉？"},{"pid":"d44bbccbceeb28646787ace513580b966323dc96","tid":2272351,"uid":34841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddc94856ac623e892982c6e17a9884bc47463a3b","tid":2272351,"uid":25582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T10:45:04.000Z","msg":"利嘉？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T00:01:31.000Z","msg":"都係附近"},{"pid":"49f065c92a1f3f70b76ad674b2d0f171b8c34fe6","tid":2272351,"uid":34841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T07:09:11.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4475e50b6f4bac428af9b8e3d9db8e7ceb0c2e","tid":2272351,"uid":34841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T14:10:08.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}